## âš™ï¸ Setup Instructions

### âœ… Step 1: Initialize Project

npm init -y

### âœ… Step 2: Install Tailwind CSS via CLI

npm install -D tailwindcss

### âœ… Step 3: Create Your Input CSS

@import "tailwindcss";

### âœ… Step 4: Start Tailwind CLI (with Watch Mode)

npx tailwindcss -i ./src/input.css -o ./src/output.css --watch

-i â†’ Input CSS file
-o â†’ Output CSS file
--watch â†’ Automatically rebuild on changes

### âœ… Step 5: Link Compiled CSS in HTML

<!-- ./src/index.html -->
<link rel="stylesheet" href="./output.css" />


